videos.description: QB Baker Mayfield connects with TE Mark Andrews for the quick score.
videos.headline: Oklahoma scores in less than a minute

videos.description: QB Baker Mayfield finds Dimitri Flowers wide open up the middle and he dances his way in from 52 yards for the score.
videos.headline: Oklahoma connects for long passing TD

videos.description: QB Zach Smith finds WR Denzel Mims for a 19-yard strike to cut the deficit.
videos.headline: Baylor gets on the board with passing TD

videos.description: RB Abdul Adams finds a hole and goes the length of the field for Oklahoma against Baylor.
videos.headline: 99 yards! Adams runs the distance for TD

videos.description: WR CeeDee Lamb never loses sight of the ball after the pass from QB Baker Mayfield is initially bobbled.
videos.headline: OU's Lamb keeps eyes on the prize for big gain

videos.description: The Sooners add to their lead after Dimitri Flowers takes the direct snap and lunges over the goal line.
videos.headline: Flowers adds a rushing TD to his day

videos.description: QB Zach Smith uses his cannon to link with Denzel Mims for a 71-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Baylor answers with long passing TD

videos.description: For the second time tonight, Baylor has a passing touchdown longer than 70 yards. Zach Smith to Chris Platt for 72 yards makes it a 3 point game.
videos.headline: Baylor opens the second half with a long passing TD

videos.description: WR Marquise Brown tried for more yards and lost the handle resulting in a fumble recovery for Baylor.
videos.headline: Turnover by OU gives Baylor momentum

videos.description: QB Baker Mayfield drops in a dime to Jeff Badet for a 48-yard strike to reclaim the lead.
videos.headline: Sooners regain the lead with passing TD

videos.description: RB Trey Sermon stays in bounds and scores on a 34-yard run and boosts lead to 11.
videos.headline: OU separates from Baylor with rushing TD

videos.description: RB Trey Sermon punches it in from 6 yards out and increases the Sooners' lead to 18.
videos.headline: Sermon gets 2nd rush TD of game

videos.description: Denzel Mims is not only able to keep an eye on the ball, but is able to keep his feet in bounds for a crazy catch.
videos.headline: Mims with an incredible juggling catch

videos.description: Baylor still has some fight after WR Denzel Mims catches his third touchdown of the night.
videos.headline: Mims adds his 3rd TD catch

videos.description: Down one score, Baylor needed an onside kick and they got it!
videos.headline: Baylor gets one last chance by recovering onside kick

videos.description: Pressure by the Sooners' defense forced a fumble and recovered it to end Baylor's comeback.
videos.headline: Oklahoma fumble recovery seals the victory
